 both nuclear matter and $^{4}$He scattering by\nconsidering two cases of $\\Lambda=450$ and $550$ MeV. The uncertainty coming\nfrom the dependence is smaller than chiral-3NF effects even at $E_{\\rm\nin}/A_{\\rm P}=175$ MeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 16:37:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Dec 2017 10:51:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
