ting galaxies in high halo masses can be\nrevealed by studying the environment of radio galaxies, thus providing new\nconstraints on galaxy formation physics at high redshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 19:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
