lity of heavy-flavour jet identification algorithms. The heavy-flavour\njet identification efficiency is measured with a precision of a few per cent at\nmoderate jet transverse momenta (between 30 and 300 GeV) and about 5% at the\nhighest jet transverse momenta (between 500 and 1000 GeV).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 19:19:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 19:48:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-10"}
