ithm in cases where the probabilistic model assumed for the data is not\nlog-concave.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Dec 2017 12:10:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 Dec 2017 10:32:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-09"}
