 statistic to a\nredshift space distorted density field, we find a significant signal in the\neigenvalues $\\Lambda_{1,2}$, suggesting that they can be used to probe the\nlarge-scale velocity field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Dec 2017 13:16:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 May 2018 17:37:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
